


02-14-2023 - Conditional Statements More


if-else statements
-if else statements in Java can be used to control the flow the program. Usually, there are multiple blocks of code that will probably be executed based on a condition.


SYNTAX:
if(condition1){
	// this block will be executed in case condition1 is true
}
else if(condition2){
	// this block will be executed in case condition2 is true
}
else{ // any other possibility
	
}
















